---
import ContentLayout from '../layouts/ContentLayout.astro';
---

<ContentLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Contact Us — Nantian Gateway"
  description="Get in touch with the Nantian Gateway community via GitHub Issues and more."
  heading="Contact Us"
  intro="The fastest way to reach the team is through our open community channels on GitHub."
>
  <section>
    <h2>Community Q&amp;A</h2>
    <p>
      For general questions, architecture discussions, sharing your deployment, or showcasing what you've built, our <a href="https://github.com/nantian-gw/gateway/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub Issues</a> tracker is the best place to start. Maintainers and community members actively answer questions here.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Bug Reports & Feature Requests</h2>
    <p>
      Found a bug or have an idea for a new feature? Please open an issue on our <a href="https://github.com/nantian-gw/gateway/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub Issues</a> tracker. Be sure to include reproduction steps, your environment details, and relevant logs so we can help you faster.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Security Reports</h2>
    <p>
      If you have discovered a security vulnerability, please do <strong>not</strong> open a public issue. Instead, follow the responsible disclosure process outlined in our <a href="https://github.com/nantian-gw/gateway/security/policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Security Policy</a> so we can address it privately.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Contributing</h2>
    <p>
      Want to help build Nantian Gateway? We welcome pull requests of all sizes. Read our <a href="/en/contributing/">Contributing Guide</a> to learn how to set up your development environment and submit your first change.
    </p>
  </section>
</ContentLayout>
